text = "[center][font_size=22][b]Reliability Indicators[/b][/font_size][/center]

[font_size=15]All the indicators of reliability or unreliability in the fake sources can be applied to anything you encounter online in real life.

[color=#f09090]Multiple negative indicators[/color] mean a source is likely unreliable, while [color=#90e0b0]multiple positive indicators[/color] show a more reliable one.

Match up the actual indicators to the werewolf sources to show why some are reliable and others are not.[/font_size]"

